      "akus": [
        {
          "ref": null,
          "body": "oṃ viṣṇave namaḥ śiraḥ oṃ jvalanāya namaḥ śikhā | oṃ viṣṇave namaḥ kavacam oṃ viṣṇave namaḥ sphuraṇaṃ diśobandhāya | oṃ huṃphaḍastram oṃ śirasi śuklo vāsudeva iti | oṃ āṃ lalāṭe raktaḥ saṃkarṣaṇo garutmān vahnis teja āditya iti | oṃ āṃ grīvāyāṃ pītaḥ pradyumno vāyumegha iti | oṃ āṃ hṛdaye kṛṣṇo 'niruddhaḥ sarvaśaktisamanvita iti | evaṃ caturvyūham ātmānaṃ kṛtvā tataḥ karma samācaret ||"
        },
        {
          "ref": null,
          "body": "āvāhanamantraḥ: mīnarūpo varāhaś ca narasiṃho 'tha vāmanaḥ | āyātu devo varado mama nārāyaṇo 'grataḥ ||"
        },
        {
          "ref": null,
          "body": "oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya namaḥ ||"
        },
        {
          "ref": null,
          "body": "oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya namaḥ ||"
        },
        {
          "ref": null,
          "body": "arghamantraḥ: oṃ trailokyapatīnāṃ pataye devadevāya hṛṣīkeśāya viṣṇave namaḥ | oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya namaḥ ||"
        },
        {
